> Width of rectangle.</li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">h</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> Height of rectangle.</li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">r</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> Radius of corner.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Draw a rounded rectangle at (x, y) coordinate of <code class=\"language-text\">w</code> width, <code class=\"language-text\">h</code> height and <code class=\"language-text\">r</code> radius corner.</p>\n<h3 id=\"gcfillroundrectx-y-w-h-r\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#gcfillroundrectx-y-w-h-r\" aria-label=\"gcfillroundrectx y w h r permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gc.fillRoundRect(x, y, w, h, r)</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">x</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> coordinate X.</li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">y</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> coordinate Y.</li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">w</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> Width of rectangle.</li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">h</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> Height of rectangle.</li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">r</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> Radius of corner.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Draw a filled and rounded rectangle at (x, y) coordinate of <code class=\"language-text\">w</code> width, <code class=\"language-text\">h</code> height and <code class=\"language-text\">r</code> radius corner.</p>\n<h3 id=\"gcdrawtextx-y-text\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#gcdrawtextx-y-text\" aria-label=\"gcdrawtextx y text permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gc.drawText(x, y, text)</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">x</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> coordinate X.</li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">y</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> coordinate Y.</li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">text</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;string></code> Text string to draw.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Draw a text at (x, y) coordinate.</p>\n<h3 id=\"gcmeasuretexttext\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#gcmeasuretexttext\" aria-label=\"gcmeasuretexttext permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gc.measureText(text)</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">text</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;string></code> Text to get text bound.</li>\n<li><strong>Returns:</strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;object></code> Text bound.\n<ul>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">width</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> Width of text.</li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">height</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> Height of text.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Get text bound (width, height) of a given text string.</p>\n<h3 id=\"gcdrawbitmapx-y-bitmap-options\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#gcdrawbitmapx-y-bitmap-options\" aria-label=\"gcdrawbitmapx y bitmap options permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gc.drawBitmap(x, y, bitmap[, options])</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">x</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> coordinate X.</li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">y</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> coordinate Y.</li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">bitmap</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;object></code> Bitmap image.\n<ul>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">width</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> Bitmap width.</li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">height</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> Bitmap height.</li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">bpp</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> Bits per pixel. Default: <code class=\"language-text\">1</code>.</li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">data</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;Uint8Array|string></code> Bitmap data. If string type is given, it should be a base64-encoded string. <em>Note that <code class=\"language-text\">Uint8Array</code> type is much faster than base64-encoded string.</em></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">options</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;object></code> Bitmap drawing options\n<ul>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">color</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> Color for 1-bit mono bitmap. Default: <code class=\"language-text\">1</code> for 1-bit bitmap and <code class=\"language-text\">0xffff</code> for 16-bit bitmap.</li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">transparent</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> Color value to be treated as transparent if defined.</li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">scaleX</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> Horizontal scale of bitmap. Default: <code class=\"language-text\">1</code>.</li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">scaleY</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> Vertical scale of bitmap. Default: <code class=\"language-text\">1</code>.</li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">flipX</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;boolean></code> Horizontal flip of bitmap. Default: <code class=\"language-text\">false</code>.</li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">flipY</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;boolean></code> Vertical flip of bitmap. Default: <code class=\"language-text\">false</code>.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Draw a bitmap image at (x, y) coordinate. The bitmap is drawn with current color in case of 1-bit bitmap.</p>\n<h2 id=\"class-bufferedgraphicscontext\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#class-bufferedgraphicscontext\" aria-label=\"class bufferedgraphicscontext permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Class: BufferedGraphicsContext</h2>\n<p>This class inherits from <code class=\"language-text\">GraphicsContext</code>.</p>\n<p>An instance of <code class=\"language-text\">BufferedGraphicsContext</code> provides graphic functions that effects to the an internal buffer, so you need to call <code class=\"language-text\">display()</code> finally to take effect on actual graphic device.</p>\n<h3 id=\"new-bufferedgraphicscontextwidth-height-options\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#new-bufferedgraphicscontextwidth-height-options\" aria-label=\"new bufferedgraphicscontextwidth height options permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>new BufferedGraphicsContext(width, height[, options])</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">width</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> Screen width of the graphic device in pixels.</li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">height</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> Screen height of the graphic device in pixels.</li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">options</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;object></code> Graphic context options.\n<ul>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">rotation</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> Rotation of screen. One of <code class=\"language-text\">0</code> (0 degree), <code class=\"language-text\">1</code> (90 degree in clockwise), <code class=\"language-text\">2</code> (180 degree in clockwise), and <code class=\"language-text\">3</code> (270 degree in clockwise).</li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">bpp</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> Bits per pixel. Currently <code class=\"language-text\">1</code> or <code class=\"language-text\">16</code> supported.</li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">display</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;function(buffer: Uint8Array)></code> A callback function to display the buffer on the graphic device.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"bgcbuffer\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#bgcbuffer\" aria-label=\"bgcbuffer permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>bgc.buffer</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;Uint8Array></code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Internal graphic buffer.</p>\n<h3 id=\"bgcdisplay\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#bgcdisplay\" aria-label=\"bgcdisplay permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>bgc.display()</h3>\n<p>Display the graphics by pushing the graphic buffer to the driver.</p>"},"allMarkdownRemark":{"nodes":[{"frontmatter":{"category":"","order":0,"slug":"__home","title":"Home"}},{"frontmatter":{"category":"","order":0,"slug":"__packages","title":"Packages"}},{"frontmatter":{"category":"root","order":0,"slug":"docs","title":"Introduction"}},{"frontmatter":{"category":"root","order":3,"slug":"docs/tutorials","title":"Tutorials"}},{"frontmatter":{"category":"root","order":2,"slug":"docs/repl","title":"REPL"}},{"frontmatter":{"category":"api","order":null,"slug":"docs/api/adc","title":"ADC"}},{"frontmatter":{"category":"api","order":null,"slug":"docs/api/board","title":"Board"}},{"frontmatter":{"category":"api","order":null,"slug":"docs/api/button","title":"Button"}},{"frontmatter":{"category":"api","order":null,"slug":"docs/api/at-command","title":"AT Command"}},{"frontmatter":{"category":"api","order":null,"slug":"docs/api/console","title":"Console"}},{"frontmatter":{"category":"api","order":null,"slug":"docs/api/digital-io","title":"Digital I/O"}},{"frontmatter":{"category":"api","order":null,"slug":"docs/api/flash","title":"Flash"}},{"frontmatter":{"category":"api","order":null,"slug":"docs/api/events","title":"Events"}},{"frontmatter":{"category":"api","order":null,"slug":"docs/api/graphics","title":"Graphics"}},{"frontmatter":{"category":"api","order":null,"slu